{"tid":684552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不獲民進黨提名出選台北市長　呂秀蓮宣布退黨","createTime":"2018-05-30T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-31T04:28:23.000Z","uid":4564,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c815b6b5edcf69d931e6a80e0cf466372a713774","tid":684552,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/30/233359_496696a4350e446ebf1cad0f03c90224.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F30%2F233359_496696a4350e446ebf1cad0f03c90224.png&h=64445892&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n台灣「九合一」選舉將於今年11月舉行。民進黨黨中央執行委員會今日通過提名立委姚文智參選。而早前曾明言有意參選的前副總統呂秀蓮，同日晚上透過辦公室發聲明退黨。民進黨表示，尊重呂秀蓮有關決定，但對此感到遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n呂秀蓮在聲明中表明與民進黨「道不同，不相為謀」，形容該黨是「一個失去黨德和黨魂的政黨」：「與其痛苦留下來，不如歸去。」<br />\n<br />\n台北市是6個直轄市中戰況最激烈的一城，至今已有10人宣布參選。除姚文智外，還有爭取連任的柯文哲、國民黨立委丁守中、前副市長邱文祥等。<br />\n<br />\n（中央社）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180530/s00004/1527683016385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180530%2Fs00004%2F1527683016385&d=nXJoC05fDDEosIck8i9fsjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=33b4592e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180530%2Fs00004%2F1527683016385&h=f82fec68\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180530/s00004/1527683016385</a>"},{"pid":"d8eb32b59d12079fccb6bc5e0860b2d96004ce6f","tid":684552,"uid":85168,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:36:15.000Z","msg":"過氣綠營人士"},{"pid":"cde07c73c9d99fee7490ed6d8098c2cea2899ba7","tid":684552,"uid":55,"like":2,"dislike":27,"score":-25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-30T15:36:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"51c27ed347a30b606b5f438274d469c35fa66d65","tid":684552,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,